      "description": "## Welcome to FreeAgent FinOps CLI\n\nThis repository provides CLI helpers for interacting with the FreeAgent API, enabling you to manage bank transactions, bills, invoices, and accounting reports programmatically.\n\n**Key Features:**\n- OAuth2 authentication with token refresh\n- Bank accounts and transactions management\n- Bills and invoices operations\n- Accounting reports (balance sheet, profit & loss)\n- Multiple output formats (plain, CSV, JSON, YAML)\n- Rate limiting and error handling\n\n**Target Users:** Developers, finance teams, and automation engineers working with FreeAgent data.",
