      "file": "scripts/fa_cli.py",
      "description": "## Main CLI Script\n\nThe `fa_cli.py` script is the heart of this project. It's a Python 3.11+ script using `uv` for dependency management.\n\n**Key Components:**\n- OAuth2 authorization code flow\n- Token refresh on 401 responses\n- Rate limit handling with backoff (429 responses)\n- Pagination support with configurable page size\n- Multiple output formats\n\n**Script Headers:** Notice the `uv` script header at the top which defines dependencies inline.",
      "line": 1,
