      "description": "## Environment Configuration\n\nThe CLI uses environment variables for configuration. Copy this file to `.env` and configure your OAuth credentials.\n\n**Required Variables:**\n- `FREEAGENT_OAUTH_ID`: Your OAuth application ID\n- `FREEAGENT_OAUTH_SECRET`: Your OAuth application secret\n- `FREEAGENT_OAUTH_REDIRECT_URI`: Must match your OAuth app settings\n- `FREEAGENT_SCOPE`: OAuth scopes (typically empty for full access)\n\n**Security:** Never commit your `.env` file â€” it's in `.gitignore`.",
