      "description": "## Ready to Contribute?\n\n**To get started:**\n1. Set up your OAuth credentials in `.env`\n2. Run `./scripts/fa_cli.py auth` to authenticate\n3. Try some CLI commands to explore the API\n4. Install pre-commit hooks: `pre-commit install`\n5. Make your changes and run `pre-commit run -a` before committing\n\n**Resources:**\n- [FreeAgent API Docs](https://dev.freeagent.com/docs)\n- [Contributing Guidelines](AGENTS.md)\n- [Code Tour Documentation](.tours/README.md)\n- [Agent Documentation](.github/agents/README.md)\n\n**Questions?** Check [CLAUDE.md](CLAUDE.md) for AI assistance or open an issue on GitHub."
